<p>If you are interested in officiating high school lacrosse in the state of Indiana please contact Clint Carter at <a href="mailto:carterch@ips.k12.in.us">carterch@ips.k12.in.us</a>. 
 Officiating lacrosse is very similar to officiating other sports. If you are interested in officiating lacrosse the Indian can help train you as well as US Lacrosse. </p>
 
 <p>To learn more about what is involved in coaching lacrosse please click here: <a href="http://www.inlaxref.org/training/">Indiana USL Chapter</a></p>
